description=Patched services.jar for razr fold 2026 stock. (1) ReconcilePackageUtils: lets org.lindroid.ui join android.uid.system despite the AOSP test-key signature (enables the Lindroid app on stock). (2) Retains DisplayManagerFlags.isExternalDisplayLimitModeEnabled()->false. Supersedes services_dispcap; disable that one.
